
Tar in lnux is used to archive the files and folders;

# tar -cvf => -c for creating
	    v for viewing the list
	    f for files show after archive done.
# ex => tar -cvf test.tar compressing/



# tar -czvf => z for compressing
# ex => tar -czvf test.tar.gz compressing/

# for viewing the tar file without extracting the content

tar -tf test.tar

-------------------------------------------------

#for extracting

tar -xvf test.tar


for gzip the compressed tar file

tar -zxvf filename.tgz

